snippet.title: Miruno Kazuki
snippet.description:
Hello, I'm Miruno Kazuki, and I create nightcore music for your enjoyment!

- New nightcore from a variety of genres!
- No comments are ignored, and I am always willing to respond to any questions you may have!
- Suggestions for songs are always welcome!

● Contact: mirunocontact@gmail.com

Thank you for visiting, and if you enjoy my work, please subscribe!
